WEBVTT

00:00:04.140 --> 00:00:08.660
ano suiheisen ga touzakatte iku

00:00:10.650 --> 00:00:16.650
aosugita sora ni wa ashita sura egakenakute

00:00:16.650 --> 00:00:22.370
iki mo dekinai kurai yodonda hito no mure

00:00:23.050 --> 00:00:29.390
boku wa itsu kara koko ni mogurikondanda

00:00:29.850 --> 00:00:36.020
kanashimi nante hakidashite mae dake mitereba iindakke

00:00:36.020 --> 00:00:41.360
sore ja totemo matomo de ira-rena

00:00:42.660 --> 00:00:49.460
subete o boku ga teki ni mawashitemo hikari o kasuka ni kanjiterunda

00:00:49.460 --> 00:00:54.810
soko made yukesou nara

00:00:55.540 --> 00:01:01.760
iki o shitakute koko wa kurushikute

00:01:01.760 --> 00:01:08.220
yami o miageru dake no boku ja ukabu houhou mo nai daibaa

00:01:08.220 --> 00:01:14.330
iki o shitemite

00:01:14.790 --> 00:01:20.820
tada no shiawase ni kidzuitara mou nido too

00:01:20.820 --> 00:01:24.910
oborenai yo...
